  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221161624792\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221161624792\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">이수한의원 식구들이&nbsp;그동안 먹은 점심 메뉴에요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be15837a2d144691.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-20\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">식당이름이 '원대구탕'이라고 용산에서 유명한곳인데</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">메뉴는&nbsp;대가리탕..이라고 저는 처음 먹어봤는데</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">생각보다 괜찮더라구요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\">얼큰하니 맛있었어요</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><p style=\"text-align: center; \" align=\"center\"><br /></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjAz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3NDE5.jyLLBlsp0JcfENRAsWTWEjvnVCEqptPHoJJVFz1B1IMg.oFKyKoea4bSZ2jnww8pIK42ubqn184_THnt4KNXJ2DQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181948950.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjAz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3NDE5.jyLLBlsp0JcfENRAsWTWEjvnVCEqptPHoJJVFz1B1IMg.oFKyKoea4bSZ2jnww8pIK42ubqn184_THnt4KNXJ2DQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181948950.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzEyMTJfMjAz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3NDE5.jyLLBlsp0JcfENRAsWTWEjvnVCEqptPHoJJVFz1B1IMg.oFKyKoea4bSZ2jnww8pIK42ubqn184_THnt4KNXJ2DQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181948950.jpg?type=w3\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ae0168322807b0a.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTI1/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3NjQ0.we97rtOgcD6hRzSnR2GX1fmqOkeE8k9nD_jLFbyUx6Ig.wVwLOHmttKOqxbMPg0ME0DmQNeyc7wpikSZd0EIzWjkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181948626.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ae0168322807b0a.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/393a5ac8087bf57d.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTM3/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3ODA2.pUg-ObYEcYd77XCMd49oaHI_dOTFHwWkSO8w_po5en4g.Xx_DRdVuq-SSDtPILeX99ws3GxpAPjSoiIBjZGVLiaEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181949378.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/393a5ac8087bf57d.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><p align=\"center\">고니..가 생긴게 좀 그래서 그렇지</p><p align=\"center\">국물은 끝내줘요&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\">저는 고니에게 익숙해지려면 아직&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\">시간이 필요할거같아요</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/494e3d68f3e95fff.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjAx/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU3OTY5.epEaAwpAYP6elKx8ZbAW74NvmdNZWfCaBoXBKf-lHuog.dnuBO7tVoR2Iej731-6pb6N5ApdKSDTBqd9l_A24WOgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181949850.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/494e3d68f3e95fff.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7027c51a3b64e7b8.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfODIg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU4MjMy.aKGYeLsyeImASvZSOZr7xARIEQCNw8fQodXnjEsLRiog.64nI_E_deMtqXsaMjoYx6K8BIljnk36syl7j9nrF6CIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181950496.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7027c51a3b64e7b8.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/13764ba78f534e57.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjk0/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU4NDE1.dgf5-b9ru5pleUwxMmUkXCqrTB51jsouz-JLxxoRYPsg.d4tj2vjmG4ZUYZDEd_F0BOQrqHymGbjmUh5ZCUO7uiMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181950124.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/13764ba78f534e57.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/189bbe34b8b0a4c3.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjU0/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU4NTkw.rrzOCMWRJxfTYPvxoeDuxjv46ELMWaqEF0UkYEryP_0g.FNMr3szHMeqrxbZB7JcfnLfuZEuYRPNDmYEbEQVUSWAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181950783.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/189bbe34b8b0a4c3.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><p align=\"center\">여기가 장사가 그렇게 잘된다고 해서</p><p align=\"center\">원장님께서 왜 장사가 잘되는지 보라고</p><p align=\"center\">일부러 데리고 간곳입니다</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">근데 진짜 손님이 바글바글</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">직원 아주머니도 너무 친절하고 좋아요</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">______________________________________________</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">여기는 숭실대 근처에있는 초밥집인데</p><p align=\"center\">여기도 사람이 바글바글</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">점심시간이고 학교근처라</p><p align=\"center\">학생들이 엄청 많았어요</p><p align=\"center\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\">메뉴는 초밥정식</p><p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e6547924bb9fc8bf.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfNSAg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU4ODAy.sQ9mRcStF_Gx69_9E2Y6KsdCMHjymgDe21ExKO9d13kg.-xjK98aBjpCHdlc0lBP0HDVDqfPzghPWKo_x73Bost8g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181951166.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e6547924bb9fc8bf.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0fa759d7f08f1d7c.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjYw/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU4OTgz.9U67R3G_rjUulMmhIVHTUs6As9voQZI3pqG-SgICzR8g.6riP_W4md2eTYOTnoTDvViCiKzCq3xTj3Va1mMAoyoAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181952003.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0fa759d7f08f1d7c.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">초밥 우동 게튀김 샐러드&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이렇게 나왔구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b4ebd12f76525676.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjY3/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU5MzIw.-vVnlyJxJA8bMERQJ7w6oolPOl2npQiQhkbvYnmFbdUg.RZ8YRZ-kbN1eluS2YtxIsnCmyIz7B3En5fzfxsiGZIUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181951579.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b4ebd12f76525676.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fb4d641743c6f7c8.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTQ3/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU5NDg4.gZUW2vcubcfwbDovrcfLFWlc5ouAsbT9LdCZAFViVu0g.PrCsF-zQ5s0ZjFYaOEQucEKFiU3-rEURUXpLHCqN5-gg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181952303.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fb4d641743c6f7c8.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d6b49798e0480f39.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjg3/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU5NjY3.fv7IiNmOt7YSIsNAyLF_aOy1YvNTV12JPz2AArhDOJgg.TPS-R26rLdQ4-dh4ljcMrRFsLLeqW7ZfAaLrnoQuhJIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_181954471.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d6b49798e0480f39.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">진짜 배부르게 먹었어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">______________________________________________</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">여기는 마포구에 있는 김치찌개 전문으로 하는 식당이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">차에서 내려서 들어가려는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">차에는 내리는 순간부터 김치찌개 냄새가 장난아닙니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">밥먹으라고 유혹하는 냄새</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b6e3d9194fe3754.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTYy/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTU5ODIx.zo3ShwvNF7uyzybD8YGAOOP6DAfeUrx7aplLzmEu1EAg.W1mGrX6q7JztDlPduC14NvopJfD6PNTX5fge6RPg9qAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182044525.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b6e3d9194fe3754.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d82ba78a6393364.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjA5/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwMTA4.Dq0_9wSYCzsxF6te5XvrzbiwTmixi1lgEKwjVxVjcTUg.OXLo0xoPtsPOvIZ4KBB12-1wIjXPQhEIg2cte8p7dosg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182045269.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d82ba78a6393364.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">김치찌개가 나왔구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">보글보글 끓기시작하면</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/755b361eee1a55fc.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTEz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwMjI3.DbatV7HJ43S3POeJGigF5WT-0r8dVtD8aNHmsqg6zxYg.QKkN0IaMQYkPC4AprK4KNtB4eboL_XIiIhg9h80J70sg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182046103.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/755b361eee1a55fc.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">라면사리 넣고 다시 보글보글 끓여줍니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">김치찜도 나옵니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">고기덩어리 큰거봐요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05665d6dd86f5d78.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTU3/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwNDA3.HtWP1bnVhcA1hCG0c-fENxrfXqmpNxnTODZ9pV0VuTAg.aqg911annn-RWOP8hJCi_cdjJFDgSopfggXCcESvf0wg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182045671.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/05665d6dd86f5d78.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e8e9973995c0e000.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfNTcg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwNjI0.1V0n4tNzKOD4Jqgn2OlEZqAk4p9DeltvMGHCR8tBSq4g.XhVsopkFRaEzXhmtapeBHZZQHgE9nr6fUJPImQuuCw4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182046544.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e8e9973995c0e000.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이렇게 고기한점이랑 김치랑 먹으면 꿀맛!!</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">______________________________________________</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">홍대에있는 '홍대교동짬뽕'이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이날은&nbsp;원장님 아이들도 함께 해서</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">인원 총 6명이었습니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">원장님 두분은 아이들과 함께 하고</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저랑 영미샘은 옆테이블에서 먹었지요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">어른들은 짬뽕, 아이들은 짜장면을 먹었는데<span>&nbsp;</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9cf58169ebeb3ecf.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"240\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:240px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjgz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwNzcy.Hq0-iEHXPyPyTKYG-AFkr0vDFbRUDERuOecNaJ3rAPYg.ZSYLCozI_HZo8KolwJuDd0sJST4XiI3Fa68rHpRXEFAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182049919.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9cf58169ebeb3ecf.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27678131d1648e55.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjcg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYwOTA3.8LXQj8TbXhVtBwuN8gRWo95ERBdtYbXjsBixlMxm_m0g.YyilNikhmw2QuYlroCW1_NBY9kxki5uJgEBumMwG_wIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182049155.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27678131d1648e55.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">탕수육도 추가했어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/517cddbc72003612.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjUg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYxMDY5.sihef2YpXV0kGo876UgISqXHDGuU1bz9EpEpVevm30Ag.ELkoDRYCs0VcfiPpPNISDk_eFQbatH3A8GEeZCElQGkg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182048721.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/517cddbc72003612.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이집 탕수육 소스는 특이했어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">계피맛이 나더라구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">부먹이 아닌 찍먹으로 먹는다하니</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이렇게 주더라구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">건포도가 들어간 탕수육도 처음봐요 ㅋ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">계피맛도 나고 건포도도 들어가서 무슨맛인지 모르시겠죠?</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">맛있었어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1389dd11db8beb41.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTMg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYxMjA2.wIA_ciJOPinsD7jLe95y8pw8ur3h_K-wp_SKANejxUMg.0k6qO7VWJWyoXuWVTKeFc7twLLRqa3x9sNR_fJOaKSEg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182050366.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1389dd11db8beb41.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">잠시후 주문한 짬뽕이&nbsp;나오고</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">이건 순두부짬뽕밥인데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">가운데 동그란 흰색이 순두부에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f1507f5bdc6783de.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjU4/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYxNDM1.6Q0_491eMbxNLpNVnFWYfJRFvheifzFTSnNJSdWieO4g.kB-Jp2nyC5-ZDoTy7p5qFLFJ-EMMhC8xZpR_cnpidkUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182049550.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f1507f5bdc6783de.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5da8069234da251f.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjIz/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYxNzk2.W0XSImUB4muaB6hsFo_1yEtyC3YaMPfm77vkd055MYEg.WQuS-lXHtW1ZFqysqqmaRIFEf_umq5c5z64N9-UP32Qg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182050720.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5da8069234da251f.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">밥한공기를 추가하고 비벼줍니다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">옆테이블에 아이들 짜장면을 못찍었어요 ;;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">사장님이 아이들 먹으라고&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">추파춥스 사탕도 주시구</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">그리고 짬뽕이 매워서 그런지..</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">아이스크림도 먹을수있게 콘과 아이스크림 &amp; 아이스크림&nbsp;스쿱이 준비되있더라구요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f2719f5ad6251742.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"427\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:427px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTIg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYxOTcz.I9KrFqCaxotdYI2jrLM9DB2WwRDwvLRqQwqZn6aoYiMg.bP8SeyR0FrabujG_BAdGTpEG4rGV3wl3UsF5Sb19GvYg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182050972.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f2719f5ad6251742.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저는 바닐라 딸리 초코맛 다 퍼왔어요&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">한겨울에 덜덜떨면서 아이스크림이라니 ㅋㅋ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">너무 맛있어요 짬뽕이</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"\">여태 먹어본 짬뽕중에는 </span>국물맛도 진하고 깊고 괜찮은거같아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">______________________________________________</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">남성역 근처에있는데 동태탕 &amp; 알탕집이에요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저는&nbsp;우리동내에서 4년이나 살았는데 처음 가봤어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f79a5403e52953b8.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTAg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYyMTE1.sdFw50z14P9KlCNwyuS_qqEuB0C41Q8H47pBAc7pzdUg.Le7yq8f29Z7xfWYJboCXLsPE7o5Ru5ITLnLc0toEi98g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182102718.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f79a5403e52953b8.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">동태탕 2인분 알탕 2인분 시켰는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">양이 엄청 많아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">4명이 먹고 또 먹었는데도 계속 남아서</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">결국에는 조금 남기고왔어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3e04bcddd9ec77f2.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMTE1/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYyMzA3.BOlQJmMmlhyis6Kka9x9N4e60eN0Ywy2lVnYlgRaz-Yg.74U_YAQaCNqbK0VEXJuUC50sopxNYZPbYrr2YW12EBsg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182103425.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3e04bcddd9ec77f2.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a6c562bbe15f2bf.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfMjY2/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYyNDg2.WHtqlKUErZrOkHkOOixq8IKDGdK79IshlLgO7W-yxw8g.JFKvbchR84H7lREbQGTix6Fkj5FAnXOkd-g0bZW2OkIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182104024.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8a6c562bbe15f2bf.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저번에 고니 먹느라 힘들었는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">고니랑 친해지려고</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">고니를 다시...... 아직은 좀 힘든거같아요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">딴생각하면서 씹었어요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e359eba3bff0318a.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" style=\"cursor: pointer;line-height: 1.5; rwidth:320px; rheight:320px;\" id=\"MjAxNzEyMTJfODcg/MDAxNTEzMDgxNTYyNjM1.5gsnpkMqsoVsZo6gZA4NujDcBcSEQ_d4EuYS7yjNwXgg.CkenInnD5nicOQHQc0BdEg4TTruj3hkztoa3K2QbfwIg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20171212_182103714.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000337E4294D8')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e359eba3bff0318a.jpg\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">알은 진짜 최고!!</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">어릴때 먹고 못먹어서</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">언젠가는 먹고싶었는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">겁나 많이 먹었네요</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">ㅎㅎㅎㅎ</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ded52c373c2db614.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-2\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br />